{"tid":918753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國關係法] 有乜理由香港關係法取消，澳門關係法仲生效","createTime":"2018-11-27T12:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T14:17:47.000Z","uid":82640,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0bca8140b0207c4bc554a98e9a9103cbbc751da","tid":918753,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"U.S.-Macau Policy Act Report<br />\n<a href=\"https://2001-2009.state.gov/p/eap/rls/rpt/35706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F2001-2009.state.gov%2Fp%2Feap%2Frls%2Frpt%2F35706.htm&d=MKIgJ7Rux3u9bR48ktVXaiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=866d8f92\" target=\"_blank\">https://2001-2009.state.gov/p/eap/rls/rpt/35706.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門：<br />\n《維護國家安全法》2009年3月3日生效，刺探國家機密已經係刑事罪行，即係你去政府問錯問題已經可以拉得。假如認定某異見者或批評者涉及相開行為，便可直接執行拘捕扣押。<br />\n自2015年起澳門政府已經將百億現金交予廣東政府投資，現時澳門大量巨額儲備已交由中國政府直屬單位手中。<br />\n珠海橫琴及澳門的邊界經常因建議原因隨意改動，包括土地及海域（如澳門大學土地），兩地人民均可自由出入對方地域。<br />\n澳門政府積極準備關閉澳門機場，使用珠海機場，放棄獨立民航系統予中國政府直屬單位。<br />\n<br />\n比起香港，澳門應該死先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2449fb3e87ca3017ca4e1f3fb14ab26fc52613","tid":918753,"uid":4964,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"澳門個關係法,一早禁左個啲高科技產品當澳門同中國一樣,所以係廢嘅"},{"pid":"dd2ba109a9c477d0e9c2f9d74aeda2e38b41c5a4","tid":918753,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"依啲鄉下地方 wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fafe7213e271f3e84e350c9be51e9c7b447a7d1","tid":918753,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"澳門人咁唔鍾意香港咁就唔好嚟我哋個機場喇"},{"pid":"8fec2e8fb268b1eb3c4ce7581e5ac